
How to run:
    make
    ./poke

This assignment implements pokemon into the game.

When you start the game, you will be prompted to select a pokemon. Once you have selected your pokemon, you can press [m] to view it in your pokedex.

When you encounter a pokemon, you will see the stats of it. To escape it, press any movement key.

When you encounter a trainer, you will be prompted to view their pokemon by pressing [p], or battle them by pressing [o]. Battling will be implemented in 1.09, however to 'defeat' the trainer you can press escape key while in the battle screen.

Code for this assignment is located in character/pokemon.